{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166150/extras/release_banner.gif?t=1725343319\" /><br>Caesar\u2019s Revenge is a <strong>die-and-retry</strong> retro FPS set in ancient Rome. Assassinated by the senate on the Ides of March, 44BC, Julius Caesar returns to exact revenge on those who betrayed him. Storm a corrupt senate in this relentless slasher. Indulge in the violence. Become the fall of Rome.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166150/extras/Roman_Setting_02.png?t=1725343319\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Thrash through murderous, <strong>high-risk gameplay</strong> with a bloodlust mechanic that rewards aggression.<br></li><li>An assortment of <strong>historic weaponry</strong> including the Gladius, Composite Bow, Sling, Spear (Hasta), Greek Fire, Sica, Falx, Fire Siphon and the mighty Scorpion!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166150/extras/walk_gif_01.gif?t=1725343319\" /><br><br></li><li><strong>Three distinct acts</strong> with more than 30 hand crafted levels across the ancient world. Slaughter your betrayers across Roman fortresses, gladiatorial arenas, untamed wilds, Babylonian gardens, unholy ruins and the depths of the underworld itself. <br></li><li>An <strong>extensive bestiary</strong> of treacherous foes to be slain, both mortal and mythological. <br><br></li><li>Scribe your skill in blood with <strong>time trials</strong>, secrets and unlockables for a higher skill ceiling and extended replayability. <br><br></li><li>Bone rattling <strong>thrash metal soundtrack</strong> recorded and performed by the developers.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166150/extras/walk_gif_02.gif?t=1725343319\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Sweet Revenge","path":